\p
\v 1  David \w went|strong="H3212"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* Ahimelech \w the|strong="H6965"\w* priest \w in|strong="H3212"\w* Nob. Ahimelech \w was|strong="H5892"\w* shaking \w with|strong="H3212"\w* fear \w when|strong="H6965"\w* \w he|strong="H3212"\w* met David, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* said \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w him|strong="H3083"\w*, “Why \w are|strong="H5892"\w* \w you|strong="H6965"\w* \w by|strong="H6965"\w* yourself \w with|strong="H3212"\w* \w no|strong="H6965"\w* \w one|strong="H5892"\w* accompanying \w you|strong="H6965"\w*?”  
