\v 11  \w The|strong="H6440"\w* \w servants|strong="H6440"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* Achish said \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w him|strong="H6440"\w*, “Isn’t \w this|strong="H1931"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w*, \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w land|strong="H6440"\w*? Isn’t \w he|strong="H1931"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w one|strong="H1931"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w they|strong="H3117"\w* sing \w about|strong="H4428"\w* \w when|strong="H3117"\w* \w they|strong="H3117"\w* dance, saying,  
