\p
\v 14  Achish said \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w his|strong="H5921"\w* servants, “\w Look|strong="H5869"\w* \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w this|strong="H3027"\w* madman! \w Why|strong="H5921"\w* \w did|strong="H5869"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w bring|strong="H3381"\w* \w him|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*?  
